revision.text:
'''Xexéu''' is a city in [[Pernambuco]], [[Brazil]]. It is located in [[Zona da Mata (coastal)|Zona da mata Pernambucana]] {{convert|143|km|abbr=on}} from the state capital [[Recife]].
==Geography==
* State: [[Pernambuco]] * Region: [[Zona da Mata (coastal)|Zona da mata Pernambucana]] * Boundaries: [[Palmares, Pernambuco|Palmares]] ('''N'''); [[Alagoas]] ('''S'''); [[Maraial]] ('''W'''); [[Água Preta]] ('''E''') * Area: {{convert|110.8|km2|abbr=on}} * Elevation: {{convert|200|m|abbr=on}} * Hydrography: [[Una River (Pernambuco)|Una]] river * Vegetation: [[Subperenifólia]] forest * Climate: Hot tropical and humid * Annual average temperature: {{convert|24.5|C|F|abbr=on}} * Distance to [[Recife]]: {{convert|143|km|abbr=on}}
==Economy==
The main economic activities in Xexéu are based in agriculture, especially [[sugarcane]].
